Due to the recent reorganization, Enron Capital & Trade Resources will be=
=20
changing its name to Enron North America Corp. effective September 1st.    =
As=20
a result, we will need to replace letterhead and business cards for all=20
affected employees at our offices here in the U.S.

There are two separate groups of employees affected by this change: first,=
=20
the employees who are now reporting into one of the global functions (i.e.,=
=20
risk management or technology); second, those employees who focus their=20
efforts on the Enron North America business. =20

Those employees reporting at the global function level should have business=
=20
cards and letterhead with Enron Corp. as the company name.  Those who=20
